---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About this personal site. 关于这个个人网站。" path="/about">
  <section class="shell" style="padding: 48px 0 96px;">
    <div style="max-width: 760px;">
      <p class="mono" style="color: var(--green); font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 14px;">ABOUT / 关于</p>
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 0.96; margin: 0 0 24px;">About</h1>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>
          This is my <strong>Personal OS</strong>. It is a simple home for my writing, life notes, ideas, and small projects.
          这里是我的个人网站，也是一个长期更新的小空间。
        </p>
        <p>
          The English is kept simple on purpose. I want it to feel clear, friendly, and easy to read, with some Chinese where it feels natural.
        </p>

        <h2>Rooms</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Blog 写作</strong>: longer essays and clear thoughts.</li>
          <li><strong>Notes 笔记</strong>: small ideas that are still growing.</li>
          <li><strong>Life 生活</strong>: memories from daily life.</li>
          <li><strong>Lab 实验</strong>: tools, demos, and small web experiments.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Colophon</h2>
        <p>
          Built with Astro. The design uses a warm paper background, clear lines, and small system-style details.
          It should feel calm enough for reading, but still a little geeky.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
